rComments: Easily one of, if not the best prof I ever had. Not sure how anyone could ever say anything bad about him. He lectures with extreme clarity and never skips over anything. He is entertaining and I actually understand course material so much better taking this course.
The Krashinky's are the best. Harry is the second best professor of all-time. Only his father is better.

Professor spent too much time congratulating himself on drawing nice graphs on the chalkboard & not enough on teaching the theory and mathematics of it all. Often confuses students with counterexamples. VERY hard final exam & difficult multiple choice.
I'm sorry, he's nothing like his father.  Does speed through material.
Very friendly and willing to help.  Sets clear objectives.  However, he tends to oversimplify material during lectures.
Very friendly just like his dad, tries his best to help but final exam was hard
very organized in lectures & funny too! but...exams were killers!!
very clear, very organized, overall very fair
Sped through lectures, exams were hard.  Overall: worst prof ever.
Final exam was a killer and MC questions very difficult. boring as a lecturer.
